{"tid":2318784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又集體炒車!]最高法院未駁回賓州訴訟 只拒絕了緊急禁令救濟 案件仍在審理中","createTime":"2020-12-09T15:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T15:14:12.000Z","uid":178875,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f5fe6fba42b3c14d7c5bbcba7e3b32c55039646","tid":2318784,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/09/php4EHe0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2Fphp4EHe0S.jpg&h=4946556c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統川普競選團隊發言人艾里斯（Jenna Ellis）。（美聯社資料照）<br />\n<br />\n2020/12/09 12:40<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國主流媒體報導，指賓州共和黨人提出訴訟要求延後、翻轉大選結果，8日遭聯邦最高法院駁回。對此，美國總統川普競選團隊發言人艾里斯（Jenna Ellis）說，記者們漏掉了重點，聯邦最高法院只拒絕了「緊急禁令救濟」（emergency injunctive relief），並沒有駁回法案，訴訟仍在審理中。<br />\n<br />\n《美聯社》等美國主流媒體報導，賓州共和黨人為扭轉總統川普敗選結果，提出訴訟主張賓州擴大進行郵寄選票作法牴觸州法，但8日遭到最高法院駁回。此案由前總統小布希提名的大法官阿利托（Samuel Alito）負責審理，阿利托被視為保守派。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">艾里斯在推特上表示，「在賓州的訴訟中，記者們漏掉了重點，最高法院只拒絕了緊急禁令救濟，並沒有駁回法案，賓州的訴訟仍在聯邦最高法院待決。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3375810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3375810&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=9d857e81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3375810&h=591cef14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3375810</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e67e1c23ff9995c81bab56570fcf8f93f1d9c10","tid":2318784,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/suppor